name: Story Without Name
description: Complete story but speaker doesn't introduce themselves
transcript: I'm calling because I desperately need assistance. I've been homeless for the past two months after being evicted from my apartment. I'm currently staying in a shelter in Los Angeles. I need help finding permanent housing and getting back on my feet. I also need medical care because I have diabetes and can't afford my medication. You can reach me at 213-555-9876. I'm really hoping someone can help me. This situation has been so difficult and stressful.
